{"tid":1284242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果廣告：國際上屢見不少的暴力抗爭，卻沒有為任何訴求爭取到理想的成果。","createTime":"2019-07-04T05:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T05:42:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9857205009cc00b2483b183d3f2da021605a10","tid":1284242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"【廣告】我們愛香港這個家  盼大家心中永存愛與和平<br />\n<br />\n黃家駒曾經向世界呼叫：「Amani, Nakupenda, Nakupenda We We.」<br />\n<br />\n剛過去的七一，大家不希望見到的暴力衝擊最終發生了。有些示威者可能會說和平示威沒有帶來任何成果，但《逃犯條例》確實暫緩在立法會二讀，在今屆會期不會重臨，這就是大家努力的成果。<br />\n<br />\n我們愛香港這個家，亦珍惜每一個年輕人，只盼大家心中永存愛與和平，在憤怒掩蓋理性的一刻，不妨哼哼：「永遠去珍惜，唯有和平與愛。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157804832032448?s=100011444132197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157804832032448%3Fs%3D100011444132197&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=71bac08b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157804832032448?s=100011444132197</a>"},{"pid":"a314414757d8f4e5af942aae58d5c693b9982e83","tid":1284242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://staticad.nextdigital.com.hk/apple/e_Peace0703/mob/facebook.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticad.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fapple%2Fe_Peace0703%2Fmob%2Ffacebook.html&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=531bb061\" target=\"_blank\">https://staticad.nextdigital.com.hk/apple/e_Peace0703/mob/facebook.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://staticad.nextdigital.com.hk/apple/e_Peace0703/mob/images/mob-landing-C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticad.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fapple%2Fe_Peace0703%2Fmob%2Fimages%2Fmob-landing-C.jpg&h=d706224d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}